{"questionId":"14475316","questionHtml":"<p>Find&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo> </mo><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>EITHER</strong></p>\n<p>attempts to integrate by substitution using&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></math>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>u</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></math>&nbsp;</strong></em>OR&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>u</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></math></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: If candidate simply states&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></math>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>, but does not attempt to substitute into their integral, do not award <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em>.</p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>∫</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>8</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></mfrac><mo> </mo><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>u</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></mfrac><mo> </mo><mo>d</mo><mi>u</mi></math>&nbsp; OR&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>∫</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>8</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><msup><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>3</mn></msup></mfrac><mo> </mo><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>3</mn></msup></mfrac><mo> </mo><mo>d</mo><mi>u</mi></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong> &nbsp; (A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>u</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mfenced><mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;</strong></em>&nbsp;OR&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mfenced><mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; (A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong><em><strong>&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\n<p>attempts to apply integration by inspection&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>4</mn><mo>∫</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></mfrac><mo> </mo><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></math></strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>×</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced><msup><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mfenced><mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; (A1)(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>Award<em> <strong>A1 </strong></em>for correct power of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;and<em> <strong>A1&nbsp;</strong></em>for&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></p>\n<p><strong>THEN</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></math>&nbsp;OR&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></math>&nbsp;(final answer must include <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></math>)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[4 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"14475316","referenceCode":"23N.1.SL.TZ2.9b","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Find ∫fx dx.","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 4]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5 —Calculus","Topic 5 —Calculus","SL 5.10—Indefinite integration, reverse chain, by substitution"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}